title: Modern Technology In Ancient Egypt? - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 12/22/17

description:
Guest host Jimmy Church and an open lines caller discuss the discovery of modern type technology in sites from ancient Egypt, and whether that's proof that civilization is far older than we have been told.
